column4: Synaptic Package Manager reports that System is Up-To-Date. bzip2 is v1.02 from 2001. According to bzip2 developers bzip2's latest version is v1.03 from 2005.
with breezy you don't have the last versions. that's intentional. that it is a version from 2001 surprises me though
How can I tell if this is Breezy vs Breety ?
